pizza my heart is a 2005 film directed by andy wolk and starring shiri appleby , michael badalucco , and eyal podell . the movie premiered july 24 , 2005 , on abc family . it tells the story of a son and daughter of two rival pizzeria owners fall in love , much to the disapproval of both families . it is a modern retelling of romeo and juliet set in modern-day verona , new jersey .